<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>üèÜ Achievement Unlocked!</title>
  <style>
    body { 
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; 
      margin: 0; 
      padding: 0; 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%); 
    }
    .container { 
      max-width: 600px; 
      margin: 0 auto; 
      background: white; 
      border-radius: 20px; 
      overflow: hidden; 
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); 
    }
    .header { 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%); 
      padding: 40px 30px; 
      text-align: center; 
      color: white; 
      position: relative;
    }
    .achievement-badge { 
      font-size: 100px; 
      margin-bottom: 20px; 
      animation: bounce 2s infinite;
    }
    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      40% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
      60% { transform: translateY(-5px); }
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 36px;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
    }
    .content { 
      padding: 40px 30px; 
      text-align: center; 
    }
    .achievement-title { 
      font-size: 32px; 
      font-weight: 700; 
      color: #333; 
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .achievement-desc { 
      font-size: 20px; 
      color: #666; 
      line-height: 1.6; 
      margin-bottom: 30px; 
    }
    .congratulations {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .cta-button { 
      display: inline-block; 
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f093fb 0%, #f5576c 100%); 
      color: white; 
      padding: 18px 35px; 
      text-decoration: none; 
      border-radius: 50px; 
      font-weight: 600; 
      font-size: 18px;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(240, 147, 251, 0.4);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .achievement-details {
      background: #f8f9fa;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      margin: 30px 0;
      border-left: 5px solid #f093fb;
    }
    .achievement-date {
      color: #888;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }
    .footer { 
      background: #f8f9fa; 
      padding: 30px; 
      text-align: center; 
      color: #666; 
      font-size: 14px; 
    }
    .celebration-banner {
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6b6b, #feca57, #48dbfb, #ff9ff3, #54a0ff);
      height: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }
    .sparkles {
      position: absolute;
      top: 20px;
      right: 20px;
      font-size: 24px;
      animation: sparkle 1.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
    }
    @keyframes sparkle {
      0% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.8); }
      100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.2); }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div style="padding: 40px 20px;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="celebration-banner"></div>
      <div class="header">
        <div class="sparkles">‚ú®</div>
        <div class="achievement-badge">{{achievementIcon}}</div>
        <h1>Achievement Unlocked!</h1>
        <div class="sparkles" style="left: 20px; right: auto;">‚≠ê</div>
      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2 class="achievement-title">{{achievementTitle}}</h2>
        <p class="achievement-desc">{{achievementDescription}}</p>
        
        <div class="congratulations">
          <strong>üéâ Congratulations {{userName}}!</strong><br>
          You've reached a new milestone in your language learning journey. Your dedication and hard work are truly paying off!
        </div>

        <div class="achievement-details">
          <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #333;">üåü Achievement Details</h3>
          <p><strong>Title:</strong> {{achievementTitle}}</p>
          <p><strong>Description:</strong> {{achievementDescription}}</p>
          <p><strong>Unlocked on:</strong> {{achievementDate}}</p>
          <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Rarity:</strong> <span style="color: #f093fb; font-weight: 600;">Special Achievement</span></p>
        </div>

        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 15px; margin: 30px 0;">
          <h3 style="margin: 0 0 10px 0;">üöÄ Keep the Momentum Going!</h3>
          <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;">You're on an amazing streak! Continue learning to unlock even more achievements and reach new heights in your language journey.</p>
        </div>
        
        <a href="{{appUrl}}" class="cta-button">Continue Learning üöÄ</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p><strong>Keep up the amazing work!</strong></p>
        <p>The {{appName}} Team is cheering you on! üéä</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px;">¬© {{year}} {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px;">Share your achievement with friends and inspire them to start learning too!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
